testsuite.name: org.apache.openwhisk.core.entity.test.ParameterEncryptionTests

testcase.name: ParameterEncryption should not have a default coder when turned off
Parameters should handle decryption of json objects
Parameters should handle decryption of json objects with null field
Parameters should drop encryption propery when no longer encrypted
Parameters should read the merged message payload from kafka into parameters
AesParameterEncryption should correctly mark the encrypted parameters after lock
AesParameterEncryption should serialize to json correctly
AesParameterEncryption should serialize to json correctly when a locked parameter is overridden
AesParameterEncryption should correctly decrypt encrypted values
AesParameterEncryption should correctly decrypt encrypted JsObject values
AesParameterEncryption should correctly decrypt encrypted multiline values
AesParameterEncryption should work if with aes256 if policy allows it
AesParameterEncryption should support reverting back to Noop encryption
No-op Encryption should not mark parameters as encrypted
